column2: # I want to create a column called game_played. when i do a group_by and summarize to get the season_ator for each player, I want to filter out those players who haven't really played many games. The reason for this is becasue if you play one game, and you have an ator of a 9, it puts you high on the list
`summarise()` has grouped output by 'player_name'. You can override using the `.groups` argument.
